creepy and scary defuse. Has office blocks, very surreal. Lights in picture 3,4 and 5 flicker. Large map for playing CS/DE in. 2nd stage. still beta, final version to come.
-STORYLINE: The Terrorists have entered offices and are planning to plant bombs to destroy evidence in a case against their leader. CTs enter from the yard via roof. They have cut the generators. Backup generator is still online so their are flickering lights.
